  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Deposit-return event: a consumer redeems an empty PET bottle at",
    "a redemption-point reverse-vending machine; the deposit recorded",
    "on the product (oec:depositReturnScheme) is settled. Modelled as",
    "an ObjectEvent with action DELETE because the trade-item",
    "instance is being decommissioned out of the consumer-facing chain",
    "and handed over to the deposit-return-scheme operator for sorting.",
    "Disposition `returned` is the CBV value for items going back",
    "through a return loop; bizStep `decommissioning` reflects that the",
    "instance is leaving normal supply-chain circulation.",
    "",
    "PPWR Reg 2025/40 Title V, Art. 50 (deposit-return systems).",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,",
    "                              euppwr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/ppwr/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
